high_descs: Go to the closest corner of a dining table that is on your left.
Pick up a banana from the diningtable.
Move to the sink that is just to the left of the diningtable.
Put the banana in the sink, rinse it out, and take it out.
Place the banana on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed-out banana on the diningtable.

high_descs: Go to the dining table to your left.
Pick up the banana on the dining table.
Turn left, walk straight past the dining table and then go to the sink to your right.
Put the banana in the sink, rinse it off and then pick it up.
Turn left, walk straight past the countertop and then go to the dining table to your left.
Put the banana on the left corner of the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed banana on a dining table.
